data.description: This end unit townhome has been well maintained, ensuring a move in ready experience. Nestled in a peaceful cul-de-sac, this home features a 3-level split with two bedrooms on the same level, a master bed suite, high ceiling and spacious atmosphere, open concept with a blend of the kitchen, dining area and living room. Lots of windows throughout the home with great natural light and a tuck under two car garage. The lower level has a spacious family room, half bath and potential to create a third bedroom. Don't forget to check out the virtual tour.
